
## For Showing Trends Over Time
Line Chart  XAxis alyas Time mandatory
Area Chart  (fills the area under the line)

## For Comparing Categories
Bar Chart  vertical/horizontal (sales by product or websites visit by country)
Column Chart
Stacked Bar/Column Chart  (composition of each category) (Total Values and the contribution of Sub Categories

## For Showing Propotions/Percentages
Pie Chart
Donut Chart
100% Stacked Bar Donut Chart

## For Showing Distibutions
Histogram
Box Plot

## For Showing Relationships
Scatter Plot

